    <item>
      <title>1MDB 将对 BSI 提起 3.94 亿美元的法律诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/1mdb-to-proceed-with-394-million-legal-claim-against-bsi</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一马发展有限公司 (1Malaysia Development Bhd.) 表示，在新加坡高等法院驳回该银行的撤销诉讼申请后，其对瑞意银行 (BSI Bank Ltd.) 的法律诉讼将继续进行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/1mdb-to-proceed-with-394-million-legal-claim-against-bsi</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 03:05:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普再次要求美国法官接手纽约封口费案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/convicted-trump-asks-us-judge-to-take-over-ny-hush-money-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普要求纽约的一名美国法官接手他“有缺陷的”州封口费刑事案件，称联邦法院才是评估曼哈顿地方检察官阿尔文·布拉格所赢得的刑事定罪的适当场所。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/convicted-trump-asks-us-judge-to-take-over-ny-hush-money-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 01:45:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
